room_title: Escape room "The Ruins of The Tukanii" by The Game Room Adventure Cafe in Sacramento
room_address: 10471 Grant Line Rd Suite 120, Elk Grove, CA 95624
room_description: The Ruins of The Tukanii once feared to have been lost have been discovered. These ruins are home to such riches, but they won't be unlocked so easily. To solve this adventure, you will need to discover the clues that unlock the secrets that lie within. You will have 60 minutes to complete your adventure!
